                  </persName>
            . I saw all that passed that night, the same as Johnson. These two men confessed before the magistrate that they took the deals.</p>
               <p>Richardson called two witnesses, who gave him a good character.</p>

               <p>Keefe called two witnesses, who gave him a good character.</p>
